## Components

- **Dremio**: Data lakehouse platform (port 9047)
- **dbt**: Data transformation tool
- **Superset**: Business intelligence platform (port 8088)
- **PostgreSQL**: Transactional database (port 5432)
- **MinIO**: S3-compatible object storage (port 9001)
- **Elasticsearch**: Search and analytics (port 9200)
